definitions.definition: A province of the Bicol Region , Luzon , Philippines ; in full, Masbate Province . Capital and largest city: Masbate City .
An island of Luzon , Philippines , the largest of three in its province; in full, Masbate Island .
A city , the capital of Masbate Province, Bicol Region , Luzon , Philippines ; in full, Masbate City .
